{"tid":1028270,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"同老豆反左面 小小野都唔肯買","createTime":"2019-02-19T11:13:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T07:45:52.000Z","uid":35361,"like":6,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"db2a2ee5513f403fecbf0fcd7f65469d158b49e6","tid":1028270,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T11:13:19.000Z","msg":"本身有打開機, 而且都打得唔錯, 平時係yahoo email我個簽名title都係叫做電競師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁做得電競師, 就好似運動員咁需要日日訓練, 所以係要日日打機keep住個狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁本身我坐緊電競椅, 但無啦啦呢2日爛左, 搞到要坐普通椅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢幾日打機即刻唔順, 場場輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我叫老豆幫手去日本城買張電競椅, 佢又依依哦哦話乜野貴又剩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/21768462_758738031000821_6336748983449632965_n.png?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=b30e6382535710c3627ff0b98f6478dd&amp;oe=5CF5747E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F21768462_758738031000821_6336748983449632965_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3Db30e6382535710c3627ff0b98f6478dd%26oe%3D5CF5747E&h=8c7e3fbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌! 我即刻開佢波, 佢都唔知電競師搵成幾百萬年薪, 到時我搵到錢一定唔會比錢佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b26fe6b6b73b1ddf643cbf79d28332b4aacbbc","tid":1028270,"uid":192581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T11:15:07.000Z","msg":"少少錢都唔肯投資 點做人老豆啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ceaeb965695b4f760141119307e6cb891c787d6","tid":1028270,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:07:11.000Z","msg":"班老野唔死 個世界唔會變好"},{"pid":"30587e47807707b85f44876cb5118b89387e74c3","tid":1028270,"uid":195438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:14:01.000Z","msg":"書房椅喎"},{"pid":"cf75bfa859f0baefbf23f5312866773e17912b49","tid":1028270,"uid":109655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:15:52.000Z","msg":"樓主可唔可以要你簽名 第日你做電競師我可以攞去賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da3903d07247bdbf09bf64d06a3d1802b448efc5","tid":1028270,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:24:30.000Z","msg":"d廢老唔識新潮流<br />\n<br />\n第時你發左達唔駛俾面佢"},{"pid":"9d753077923928d0d1ed598ca43395a1fb083f41","tid":1028270,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da3903d07247bdbf09bf64d06a3d1802b448efc5","tid":1028270,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:24:30.000Z","msg":"d廢老唔識新潮流<br />\n<br />\n第時你發左達唔駛俾面佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:53:30.000Z","msg":"你岩"},{"pid":"fc76e084b145ec60a22b2852228aa1c89cfcc218","tid":1028270,"uid":43061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:57:24.000Z","msg":"比FAKER年薪你老豆睇啦..<br />\n我比完之後<br />\n我老豆即刻幫我換晒新機 新鍵盤 新MON 新滑鼠 新電腦台"},{"pid":"be36f9511ba757afc7255aee34949dffd584220c","tid":1028270,"uid":164477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:23:38.000Z","msg":"以前我老豆都係咁<br />\n依家佢見我做到電莖師之後 成日主動問我洗唔洗買電莖設備"},{"pid":"cffd3e747211ac55931fac366439753cf87eef58","tid":1028270,"uid":77769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:45:52.000Z","msg":"有無用法國麵包打你老豆？"}]}